raw_text = "~ start
Naomi: Heya!
Naomi: Hope I'm not catching you at a bad time!
Player: Hi Naomi
Naomi: 👋😊
Naomi: Sorry for texting you so late!!
Naomi: I got loads of work to do especially this week
Naomi: How's Mabel?
Player: She's doing good
Player: Busy studying hard
Naomi: Glad to hear that
Naomi: Well I wanted to ask you something kinda out of the blue
Player: What is it?
Naomi: Well... Would you consider joining our lil Photography club?
Naomi: I know Mabel's already set to sign up!
Naomi: Could I perhaps trouble you with the sign up process 😇
Player: I was thinking of joining actually!
Naomi: That's such a relief to hear!
Player: I'm not that good at photography 😆
Naomi: It's okay! We teach from the start!
Naomi: And we typically work in pairs so you and Mabel get to spend extra time together!
- I'd like that a lot!
	Player: I'd like that a lot!
	Player: Feels like we could have a lot of fun
	Naomi: It really is!
- Could I pair with you as well? [#redheart]
	Player: Could I pair with you as well?
	Naomi: I don't see why not
	Naomi: We don't have strict pairings, they're by task but
	Naomi: I love that you'd like to pair with me hehe 🥰
	Naomi: img: naomi/6
	Naomi: Look, I'm all embarassed haha
Naomi: Alright, as for the sign up task
Naomi: Caleb can assist you with it!
Player: Sign up task?
Naomi: Yea! Every club has a registration task
Naomi: They're usually pretty simple and to make sure the students aren't there to just take up the weekly grant!
Player: Oh there's a grant?
Naomi: Yes! You'll receive it once a week
Player: That's a nice bonus
Naomi: It is!
Naomi: Oh right, the task!
Naomi: You'll need to take a photograph or picture of something that interests you
Naomi: Extra points for lighting and image clarity as well as themes!
Naomi: Your submission will remain confidential and won't be shared with anyone unless you share it yourself
Naomi: Catch all that?
Player: Yep!
Naomi: I'll be assisting Mabel with her submission!
Naomi: Would you be available this afternoon for Caleb to assist you?
- I should be!
	set Story.flag = \"CalebAssist\"
	Player: I should be!
	Naomi: Great! Caleb is going to walk you through everything
	Naomi: Don't worry! It's not so hard and you can even use your phone
	Naomi: Between us, it should be a breeze because he's the best at it!
	Naomi: He's a lot more thorough than I am since I'm quite busy with admin work 😊
	Player: I'm in good hands
	Naomi: You are!
- I'd rather you assist me [#redheart]
	set Story.red_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"NaomiAssist\"
	Player: I'd rather you assist me
	Naomi: 😊
	Naomi: Hmm, I could ask Caleb to swap with me
	Naomi: Ok sure!
	Naomi: Sounds good to me!
	Naomi: So I'll come by this evening?
	Naomi: Any ideas on what you want to submit?
	Player: No idea!
	Naomi: That's fine too, we can take a little walk and see what we can find
	Naomi: Deal? 😊
	Player: Deal! 👍
Naomi: Good luck on your application!
Player: Thanks!
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
